name: Benedetto Fashion Compass
description:
Our T shirts are now on sale! This is our Compass Shirt, which has a nice slim fit and lots of details! 

Which way is home? Our Home is Copenhagen as we started the Benedetto brand there. So where is your home? Find your home with the Benedetto compass shirt.

You’ll se a very detailed compass design on the shirt. We found it very important to point out where we started; therefor we called it Benedetto Copenhagen. Beside that you’ll se the Triangle of Benedetto and our Benedetto Fashion Logo.

Price: 250 DKK

name: Benedetto Fashion Big B
description:
Our T shirts are now on sale! This is our Big B Shirt, which has a nice slim fit and lots of details!

The Big B is what starts our Brand name Benedetto Fashion. We find this shirt simple and elegant. We think it will fit very well under a cardigan or a blazer. But you can also wear just the shirt in the nice summer weather. Your choice!

The design has a lot of details with the big B, which is divided in two so you see the year Benedetto was founded. As well as the Benedetto underline where the d is changed with the greek letter delta which is a triangle. On the back you see the Benedetto triangle and our logo.

Price: 250 DKK
